createDiagrams.title: Samee Jaantusoyin
createDiagrams.prompt: I tus sida aad u samayn karto jaantusoyin iyo qulqul-jaantusoyin. Noocyada habsocodka, socodsiinta, ama nidaamyada maxaad iga caawin kartaa inaan arko? I sii tusaalooyin.

draftContent.title: Qor Nuxur Xirfadleh
draftContent.prompt: Caawimaad baan u baahnahay qorista dukumentiyo xirfad leh - iimayllada, warbixinaha, soo koobidda. Ma i tusin kartaa tusaalooyin sida aad ugu caawin karto noocyada kala duwan ee qoraalka ganacsiga?

analyzeInformation.title: Falanqee Macluumaadka
analyzeInformation.prompt: Sidee ayaad iga caawin kartaa falanqaynta xogta ama macluumaadka? I tus siyaabo kala duwan oo aad ku kala saari karto tirooyinka, hesho qaababka, ama ka soo saarto fikrado dukumentiyo ama xog-uruuryo.

planOrganize.title: Qorshe & Habeyn
planOrganize.prompt: Ma i caawin kartaa qorshaynta mashruucyada ama habeynta shaqada? I sii tusaalooyin sida aad u samayn karto jadwalada, ajendayaasha, ama qorshooyinka mashruuca oo leh qaab-dhismeedyo kala duwan.

brainstormIdeas.title: Hal-abuurka Fikradaha
brainstormIdeas.prompt: Waxaan rabaa inaan hal-abuuro xalal dhibaato. I tus sida aad u qaabayso fikir hal-abuurka iyo sameynta fikradaha - noocyada su'aalaha maxaad weydiin lahayd iyo sidee ayaad u sahamisaa suurtagalnimada?

buildPresentations.title: Samee Bandhigyada
buildPresentations.prompt: Sidee ayaad iga caawin kartaa sameynta bandhigyada? I tus tusaalooyin qaab-dhismeedyo bandhigyo oo kala duwan, soo jeedinno muuqaal, iyo sida aad u habeeyso macluumaadka daawadayaal kala duwan.

workWithCode.title: La shaqee Koodka
workWithCode.prompt: Ma i caawin kartaa koodaynta ama qoraalada? I tus tusaalooyin - hadduu yahay qorista kood cusub, hagaajinta dhibaatooyinka, ama sharaxaadda sida wax u shaqeeyaan tallaabo tallaabo.

decisionSupport.title: Taageerada Go'aanka
decisionSupport.prompt: Waxaan u baahnahay inaan sameeyo go'aan laakiin ma hubo sida aan u qiimeeyo xulashooyinkayga. Ma i tusin kartaa qaab-dhismeedyo ama habraaco kala duwan oo aad isticmaasho si aad uga fikir doorashooyinka?

summarizeSynthesize.title: Soo Koob & Isku gee
summarizeSynthesize.prompt: Sidee ayaad ugu caawisaa soo koobidda dukumentiyo dhaadheer ama isku geynta macluumaadka ilo badan? I tus tusaalooyin qaababka soo koobidda kala duwan iyo heerarka faahfaahinta.

explainTopics.title: Sharax Mawduucyada Adag
explainTopics.prompt: Ma sharxi kartaa fikradaha adag erayo fudud? I tus sida aad u kala jabiso fikradaha adag, isticmaasho tusaalooyin la mid ah, oo u habeeyso sharaxaadaha heerarka aqoonta kala duwan.

createSchedules.title: Samee Jadwalada
createSchedules.prompt: Caawimaad baan u baahnahay habeynta waqtiga iyo sameynta jadwalada. I tus siyaabo kala duwan oo aad u habeyn karto ajendayaasha, jadewalada, ama qorshooyinka ku salaysan waqtiga oo leh tusaalooyin.

agents.description: Samee oo maamul wakiilada AI ee gaarka ah oo leh awoodaha gaarka ah. Wakiiladan waxay ku shaqeeyaan qaybta MSF AI Assistant Foundry.
agents.advancedFeatureTitle: Astaanta Horumarsan - Waxay u Baahan Tahay Iskaashi Kooxda Farsamada ee Kaaliyaha AI
agents.advancedFeatureWarning: Wakiilada gaarka ah waxay kaliya la shaqeeyaan qaybta MSF AI Assistant Foundry. Aqoonsiyada wakiilka waa in ay sameeyaan kooxda farsamada ee Kaaliyaha AI qaybtan gaarka ah oo lagula xiriiro ka hor inta aan la isticmaalin.

agents.noAgentsDescription: Samee wakiilkaaga koowaad ee gaarka ah si aad u ballaariso awoodaha AI oo leh qalab iyo habdhawr gaar ah.

gpt_4_1.name: GPT-4.1
gpt_4_1.description: Moodel AI ah oo ku shaqeeya GPT-4.1 oo leh raadinta shabakadda waqtiga dhabta ah iyada oo loo maro Bing. Wuxuu bixiyaa macluumaad cusub, hubinta xaqiiqada, iyo ogaanshaha dhacdooyinka hadda. Ugu wanaagsan cilmi baarista u baahan macluumaad dhow, falanqaynta wararka, iyo xaqiijinta xaqiiqada.

gpt_5_2.name: GPT-5.2
gpt_5_2.description: Moodel-ka ugu horumarsan ee OpenAI, oo ku fiican caqli-galinta adag, sameynta koodka, iyo xallinta dhibaatooyinka farsamada. Ugu wanaagsan hawlaha falanqaynta, caqabadaha barnaamijyada, cilmi baarista, iyo sharaxaadaha faahfaahisan. Wuxuu taageeraa dadaalka caqli-galinta la habeyn karo iyo faahfaahinta jawaabta.

gpt_5_mini.name: GPT-5 Mini
gpt_5_mini.description: Nooc ka degdeg badan oo kharash yar ee GPT-5, oo loo hagaajiyey xawaaraha iyadoo la ilaalinayo tayada sare. Ku habboon hawlaha maalinlaha ah, su'aalaha degdega ah, wadista qalabka, iyo codsiyada u baahan waqtiyada jawaabta ee degdega ah. Isku dheelitir wanaagsan oo waxqabad iyo waxtarnimo.

gpt_5_2_chat.name: GPT-5.2 Chat
gpt_5_2_chat.description: Nooc gaar ah oo GPT-5.2 ah oo loo hagaajiyey isdhexgalka wada hadalka iyo caqliga dareenka. Wuxuu ku fiican yahay xiriirka naxariista, taageerada caafimaadka maskaxda, qoraalka hal-abuurka, hal-abuurka fikradaha, iyo wada hadalka dabiiciga ah. Ugu wanaagsan wada hadalka caadiga ah, xaaladaha la-talintu, iyo hawlaha u baahan ogaanshaha dareenka.

o3.name: o3
o3.description: Moodel-ka caqli-galinta ugu horumarsan ee OpenAI oo leh awoodaha xallinta dhibaatooyinka ee guuldarrada ah. Wuxuu ku fiican yahay xisaabta adag, caqli-galinta saynis, caqabadaha koodaynta, iyo hawlaha caqliga ee tallaabo badan. Daaqadda macnaha 200K oo la balaariyey. Wuxuu taageeraa xakamaynta dadaalka caqli-galinta.

llama_4_maverick.name: Llama 4 Maverick
llama_4_maverick.description: Moodel degdeg ah oo kharash yar ah ee Meta. Ku wanaagsan hawlaha maalinlaha ah sida qoraalka, soo koobidda, iyo caawimaadda koodaynta aasaasiga ah. Isku dheelitir wanaagsan oo xawaare iyo tayad ah shaqada joogtada ah.

deepseek_r1.name: DeepSeek-R1
deepseek_r1.description: Khabiir caqli-galin ah oo muujiya shaqadiisa tallaabo tallaabo. Aad u wanaagsan dhibaatooyinka xisaabta, halxiraalada caqliga, iyo fahamka fikradaha adag. Arag sida uu uga fikirayo dhibaatooyinka waqtiga dhabta ah.

deepseek_v3_1.name: DeepSeek-V3.1
deepseek_v3_1.description: Moodel awood leh oo dhinac walba ah gaar ahaan ku wanaagsan koodaynta iyo qoraalka farsamada. Ku wanaagsan hagaajinta koodka, qorista dukumentiyada, iyo sharaxaadda fikradaha farsamada. Dhakhso iyo la isku halleyn karo shaqada horumarinta.

grok_3.name: Grok 3
grok_3.description: Moodel hab badan oo ka yimid xAI oo lagu yaqaan jawaabaha qoto dheer. Ku wanaagsan doodaha furan, mashruucyada hal-abuurka, iyo wajahista dhibaatooyinka adag.

claude_opus_4_5.name: Claude Opus 4.5
claude_opus_4_5.description: Moodel-ka ugu awooda badan ee Anthropic oo leh caqli-galin gaara ah, koodayn, iyo awoodaha hal-abuurka. Ugu wanaagsan falanqaynta adag, cilmi baarista, iyo hawlaha u baahan faham qoto dheer.

claude_sonnet_4_5.name: Claude Sonnet 4.5
claude_sonnet_4_5.description: Moodel Claude ah oo dheellitiran oo bixiya waxqabad wanaagsan oo koodayn, falanqayn, iyo hawlaha hal-abuurka ah. Ku wanaagsan isticmaalka maalinlaha ah oo leh waqtiyada jawaabta ee degdega ah.

claude_opus_4_1.name: Claude Opus 4.1
claude_opus_4_1.description: Jiilka hore ee moodel-ka Claude Opus. Aad u wanaagsan hawlaha koodaynta ee adag, falanqaynta faahfaahisan, iyo fahamka qoto dheer.

claude_haiku_4_5.name: Claude Haiku 4.5
claude_haiku_4_5.description: Moodel Claude ah oo degdeg ah oo kharash yar ah oo loo hagaajiyey hawlaha dhakhsaha badan. Ku wanaagsan su'aalaha fudud, soo koobidda, iyo codsiyada tiro badan.

searchMode.noSearchDescription: Jawaabaha ugu degdega ah oo aan lahayn awooda raadinta shabakadda. Wada hadalkaaga oo dhan wuxuu ku jiraa browserkaaga - waxba daruuraha laguma kaydiyo.
searchMode.viewDetailsBelow: Faahfaahin dheeraad ah, arag qulqulka farsamada ee hoose.
searchMode.legendNoSearch: Browserkaaga (kaydi maxalli) | Server-ka Kaaliyaha AI | Azure OpenAI (xaalad la'aan)
searchMode.privacyDescription: Wuxuu isticmaalaa raadinta shabakadda marka loo baahdo laakiin waa gaabsi sababtoo ah tallaaboyin badan ayaa ku jira. Kaliya su'aalaha raadinta ayaa lagu kaydiyaa Azure - wada hadalkaaga oo dhan wuxuu ku jiraa browserkaaga.
searchMode.legendPrivacy: Browserkaaga (kaydi maxalli) | Server-ka Kaaliyaha AI | Azure AI Foundry (su'aalaha raadinta oo keliya) | Azure OpenAI (xaalad la'aan)
searchMode.foundryDescription: Jawaabaha dhakhsaha badan oo leh awooda raadinta shabakadda oo ku dhisan. Wada hadalkaaga oo dhan waxaa lagu kaydiyaa database-ka Azure AI Foundry, maaha kaliya browserkaaga.
searchMode.legendFoundry: Browserkaaga (kaydi maxalli) | Server-ka Kaaliyaha AI | Wakiilka Azure AI Foundry (kaydiyaa wada hadalka oo dhan)
searchMode.whyTheseOptionsText1: Kuwan waa hab-raacyada raadinta ee la heli karo ka dib markii Azure uu joojiyey API-ga Bing Search, kaasoo Kaaliyaha AI uu markii hore ku tiirsan yahay.
searchMode.whyTheseOptionsText2: Kooxdu waxay si firfircoon u sahamiyaan beddelada raadinta ee asturnaanta diiradda leh. Labada xulashaba waxay isticmaalaan awoodaha raadinta ee Azure AI Foundry laakiin waxay ku kala duwan yihiin inta xogta wada hadalka la wadaago.
searchMode.azureDeprecatedBingApi: Azure wuxuu joojiyey API-gooda Bing Search
searchMode.footerNote: Labada habba waxay ku kaydiyaan wada hadalkaaga si maxalli ah browserkaaga. Waxaad beddeli kartaa habka waqti kasta dejinta moodel-ka.

dropdown.searchTooltip:
Fur raadinta shabakadda fariin kasta.

Wuxuu bixiyaa macluumaad cusub iyada oo la adeegsanayo gelitaanka Bing shabakadda waqtiga dhabta ah.
dropdown.attachTooltip:
Ku lifaaq faylal, sawirro, ama cod/fiidiyow.

Qaababka la taageerayo:
‚Ä¢ Sawirro: JPEG, PNG, GIF, WebP (5MB ugu badan, ilaa 10)
‚Ä¢ Dukumentiyo: PDF, DOCX, XLSX, PPTX, TXT, MD (10MB ugu badan, ilaa 3)
‚Ä¢ Xog: CSV, JSON, XML, YAML (10MB ugu badan, ilaa 3)
‚Ä¢ Kood: PY, JS, TS, JAVA, C, CPP, GO, iwm. (10MB ugu badan, ilaa 3)
‚Ä¢ Cod/Fiidiyow: MP3, WAV, MP4, WebM (25MB ugu badan, 1 fayl)

Wadarta: 10 fayl, 50MB ugu badan
dropdown.transcribeTooltip:
Soo geli faylal cod ama fiidiyow ah si loo qoro.

Qaababka la taageerayo: MP3, MP4, WAV, WebM, M4A, MPEG, MPGA
Cabbirka ugu badan: 25MB

Qoristaanku wuxuu si toos ah u dhacaa markaad dirto fariinta.
dropdown.translateDocumentTooltip:
U turjum dukumentiyo luqad kale.

Qaababka la taageerayo: Word, Excel, PowerPoint, PDF, HTML, TXT
Cabbirka ugu badan: 40MB

Wuxuu taageeraa 80+ luqadood oo leh faylal erayga ikhtiyaariga ah.
